item.comments: Is anyone carpooling from Brookline. I live in Brookline but sold my car living in the city. Let me know. I'd love to attend. I'll pay for gas expenses.
Sorry to miss it. I just got a gig for that night.
Have to babysit my 8 month old granddaughter and my daughter is late getting home ... maybe next time.
Sorry, I had a lot of things to get done today and I got way behind due to some unforseen issues that came up. I hope you all have a fabulous time and I get to meet you next month.
three of us will be there. Do I bring any food? drink? Let me know.
Looking forward to meeting new friends!
Would like to come tonight. How will I not know if i'm on waiting list?
Trish, you have got to make buying a ticket simpler (accomplishable), and the price plain to see.
